  <scopecontent id="aspace_60b9a8b39a38879ddfebd9c00468e4e2">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Includes correspondence and printed material relating to the formation of the Oral History Association and the conduct of oral history colloquia; correspondence related to the Oral History Program at Cornell University, directed by Gould P. Colman; projects undertaken or proposed; financial records; payrolls; travel records; records relating to the Sarah Diamant film project; and seminars, talks, and papers on oral history by Colman.</p>  </scopecontent>
